    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a few imperfections. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior has moderate wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and drives, though it will likely need a suspension tune-up and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a reliable workhorse for anyone looking for transportation at an affordable price point.",
