    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of life left? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s a reliable choice that shows some honest character from its time on the road, making it perfect for someone who appreciates a car with a story to tell. It's a solid, functional option for your daily commutes!",
